{
  "$description": "| What does this do? | Ensure multifactor authentication is enabled for all users in administrative roles |\n| Why should you use this? | Ensures user accounts holding administrative roles are secured with multi-factor authentication. |\n| What is the end-user impact? | None. |\n| Learn more | [All users MFA strength](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/entra/identity/conditional-access/policy-all-users-mfa-strength) |",
